data.description:
IMAGINE your very own piece of PARADISE in Eastern Tennessee!  Surround yourself with your very own waterfall, 3 flowing creeks, and a SPRING that even brings fresh spring water into your home YEAR ROUND!  Listen as the sound of nature dances all around you and heals your spirit.  Keep your eyes peeled as wildlife of all kinds knocks on your doorstep and frolics in the six and a half acres that surround you on this lulling wooded softly sloping hillside. 
The main home on the property features TWO levels of gorgeous front decks that beckon you to sit outside and listen to your very own waterfall and birds singing in the trees.  Its history dates back to when it originally was a Mill House and now transformed into a warm, cozy home.  Inside features rustic and vintage touches that accentuate the overlap of classic and contemporary, with a highly-functional kitchen and wooden and gas stoves that state self-sufficiency is #1 on the list.  Three full stories allow for functionality and growth.
The neighboring 1200 square foot guest house features 4 bedrooms and a compostable toilet, and gives an open edge to create a homestead or just appreciate the convenience to have separate lodgings to family or guests.
Across the drive, a huge 48' x 56' workshop and 12' x 33' greenhouse also add a farm-feel to this uniquely one-of-a-kind property and give it so much versatility already, with plenty of room to still add to it if needed!
Get your pre approval letter ready and contact the listing agent today to schedule your private showing!  Make this piece of history your very own PARADISE to enjoy EVERYDAY!!
